query:
SELECT id, name, 
  CASE 
    WHEN mapData IS NULL THEN 'NULL'
    ELSE 'HAS_DATA'
  END as status,
  date
FROM trip_routes 
WHERE tripId = 30001 
ORDER BY date, id;
